ion></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.4306em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.1132em;\">τ</span></span></span></span> 阶马\n尔科夫模型，特殊的，一阶马尔科夫模型如下：</p>\n<p v-pre class='katex-block'><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><semantics><mrow><mi>P</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><msub><mi>x</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mo>…</mo><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><msub><mi>x</mi><mi>T</mi></msub><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo>=</mo><munderover><mo>∏</mo><mrow><mi>t</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mi>T</mi></munderover><mi>P</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><msub><mi>x</mi><mi>t</mi></msub><mo>∣</mo><msub><mi>x</mi><mrow><mi>t</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msub><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mtext>  when </mtext><mi>P</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><msub><mi>x</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>∣</mo><msub><mi>x</mi><mn>0</mn></msub><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo>=</mo><mi>P</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><msub><mi>x</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">.</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">P(x_1, \\ldots, x_T) = \\prod_{t=1}^T P(x_t \\mid x_{t-1}) \\ \\\n\\text{when } P(x_1 \\mid x_0) = P(x_1).\n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">P</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.3011em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.55em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"heigh