</span></span></span></span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p>假如说一个序列满足一阶马尔科夫模型，那么我们就可以观察很短的一个历史，就可以计算\n下去，这是一种很好的性质。</p>\n<p>接下来我们实践一下</p>\n<div class=\"language-python line-numbers-mode\" data-highlighter=\"shiki\" data-ext=\"python\" style=\"--shiki-light:#393a34;--shiki-dark:#dbd7caee;--shiki-light-bg:#ffffff;--shiki-dark-bg:#121212\"><pre class=\"shiki shiki-themes vitesse-light vitesse-dark vp-code\" v-pre=\"\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#A0ADA0;--shiki-dark:#758575DD\"># 生成时间序列数据，采用的是正弦波+一个随机噪声</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">T </span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">=</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#2F798A;--shiki-dark:#4C9A91\"> 1000</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">time </span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">=</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\"> torch</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">.</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">arange</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">(</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#2F798A;--shiki-dark:#4C9A91\">1</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">,</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\"> T </span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\">+</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#2F798A;--shiki-dark:#4C9A91\"> 1</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">,</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\"> dtype</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">=</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">torch</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">.</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#393A34;--shiki-dark: