ue\" style=\"counter-reset:line-number 0\"><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div></div></div><p>接下来我们整合所有的功能为一个函数，这个函数会返回词元索引列表，以及词表，这里首\n先为了简化之后的训练，我们选择字符词元化</p>\n<div class=\"language-python\" data-highlighter=\"shiki\" data-ext=\"python\" style=\"--shiki-light:#393a34;--shiki-dark:#dbd7caee;--shiki-light-bg:#ffffff;--