</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">O</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.22222em;\">Y</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p>反向传播的时候根据链式法则，可以发现会出现多个参数矩阵连乘的现象，这样的话就会出\n现梯度爆炸或者梯度消失现象。这个时候我们就需要梯度裁剪来稳定地训练</p>\n<p v-pre class='katex-block'><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"bold\">g</mi><mo>←</mo><mi>min</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mrow><mo fence=\"true\">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mfrac><mi>θ</mi><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">∥</mi><mi mathvariant=\"bold\">g</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">∥</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo fence=\"true\">)</mo></mrow><mi mathvariant=\"bold\">g</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">.</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\mathbf{g} \\leftarrow \\min \\left( 1, \\frac{\\theta}{\\|\\mathbf{g}\\|} \\right) \\mathbf{g}.\n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6389em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathbf\" style=\"margin-right:0.01597em;\">g</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">←</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:2.4em;vertical-align:-0.95em;\"></span><span class=\"mop\">min</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\"><span class=\"delimsizing size3\">(</span></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><spa