pan class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p>我们找到了生成一串序列的方法</p>\n<p>接下来我们正式介绍一下马尔科夫条件：在自回归模型中，只要我们能够找到一个时间跨度\n<span v-pre class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>τ</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\tau</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.4306em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.1132em;\">τ</span></span></span></span> 使得其近似正确，那么我们就称这个序列满足马尔科夫条件，称之为 <span v-pre class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>τ</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\tau</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.4306em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.1132em;\">τ</span></span></span></span> 阶马\n尔科夫模型，特殊的，一阶马尔科夫模型如下：</p>\n<p v-pre class='katex-block'><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><semantics><mrow><mi>P</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><msub><mi>x</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mo>…</mo><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><msub><mi>x</mi><mi>T</mi></msub><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo>=</mo><munderover><mo>∏</mo><mrow><mi>t</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mi>T</mi></munderover><mi>P</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><msub><mi>x</mi><mi>t</mi></msub><mo>∣</mo><msub><mi>x</mi><mrow><mi>t</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msub><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mtext>  when </mtext><mi>P</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><msub><mi>x</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>∣</mo><msub><mi>x</mi><mn>0</mn></msub><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo>=</mo><mi>P</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><msub><mi>x</m