:#C98A7D77\">'</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">,</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#2F798A;--shiki-dark:#4C9A91\"> 10</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">,</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\"> net</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">,</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\"> vocab</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">,</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\"> try_mps</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">()))</span></span></code></pre>\n<div class=\"line-numbers\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"counter-reset:line-number 0\"><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div></div></div><p>发现预测出来了奇怪的东西，这是因为我们的模型还没训练！</p>\n<h3 id=\"_3-梯度裁剪\" tabindex=\"-1\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#_3-梯度裁剪\"><span>3. 梯度裁剪</span></a></h3>\n<p>TODO：这里不大懂，先照抄下来</p>\n<p>不难发现，RNN在时间步过长的时候，仍然会出现梯度消失 or 梯度爆炸的现象，具体如\n下：</p>\n<p>我们首先回顾多层感知机的梯度消失是如何产生的，考虑一个具有 <span v-pre class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>n</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.4306em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span></span></span></span> 个隐藏层的DNN，前\n向传播的时候第 <span v-pre class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>i</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">i</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6595em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">i</span></span></span></span> 个隐藏层的输出作为第 <span v-pre class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>i</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">i+1</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.7429em;vertical-align:-0.0833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">i</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span></span></span></span> 个隐藏层的输入。</p>\n<p v-pre class='katex-block'><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>H</mi><mi>n</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><mi>ϕ</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><msub><mi>W</mi><mi>n</mi></msub><msub><mi>H</mi><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msub><mo>+</mo><msub><mi>b</mi><mi>n</mi></msub><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mspace linebreak=\"newline\"></mspace><mi>O</mi><mo>=</mo><msub><mi>W</mi><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msub><msub><mi>H</mi><mi>n</mi></msub><mo>+</mo><msub><mi>b</mi><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msub><mspace linebreak=\"newline\"></mspace><mi>L</mi><mi>o</mi><mi>s</mi><mi>s</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>l</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>O</mi><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>Y</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow><annotation enc